00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:06.340
are sympathetic to the plight of migrants and asylum seekers

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.000
and I welcome them.

00:00:08.001 --> 00:00:10.781
But they expect it to be done in a fair and equitive manner

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:11.920
open to.

00:00:11.921 --> 00:00:16.081
