00:00:16.082 --> 00:00:18.281
So I welcome and this package

00:00:18.282 --> 00:00:20.341
I think to bring coordination

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:22.400
in line with our obligations

00:00:22.401 --> 00:00:24.901
on the international treaties and conventions

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.480
and will ensure that there's a cohesive and proper manner

00:00:28.481 --> 00:00:31.261
in which asylum seekers are assist.

00:00:31.480 --> 00:00:34.840
