00:00:34.841 --> 00:00:37.121
legal and illegal, and stay here indefinitely,

00:00:37.122 --> 00:00:39.561
that's upsets people and that's understandable.

00:00:39.562 --> 00:00:43.141
They expected to be done and now we can do it in solidarity.

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:48.100
And I think once we do that and every member states places part,

00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:50.620
we will head to have a proper structure

00:00:50.720 --> 00:00:55.020
